=head2 assert_topic_editor

 assert_topic_editor {topic_id}

If there is no user logged in or the logged user
has no editor capabilities on the specified topic,
redirects the HTTP query to the C<ADMIN> template.
As all _assert_ templates, it does the redirection
aborting further template execution.

=cut
{-assert|{-is_topic_editor|$0}|ADMIN}
